    "You can configure access using [Data Explorer](#data-explorer) or [SQL editor](#sql-editor).",
    "### Data explorer -Click the <Data Icon> **Data** in the sidebar.",
    "-In the drop-down list at the top right... *Please note these settings are applicable to all products, if you'd like to change these settings on a product level, you can do so in the 'Catalog Synchronization' tab.",
    "# API Token This is where you will enter the API token provided by Faire.",
    "Once entered, you will also receive a message to confirm that the connection is confirmed between Faire and Prestashop."
